Ormond Lanes is a 40 lane bowling center dedicated to entertaining all generations. Our staff is here to assist you from the moment you walk through our doors.

We offer bowling birthday parties, youth bowling leagues, adult bowling leagues (including seniors only), corporate packages, Free Wi-fi and great specials!. We now have 55 inch monitors around the center so you can root your favorite team on. A state of the art- redemption arcade and our electrifying lightning strikes is coming soon.
